<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.12">
<l>maittaṭaṅ kaṇṇi yacōtai vaḷarkkiṉṟa</l>
<l>ceyttalai nīla niṟattuc ciṟuppiḷḷai</l>
<l>neyttalai nēmiyum caṅku nilāviya</l>
<l>kaittalaṅ kaḷvantu kāṇīrē kaṉaṅkuḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with golden earrings, come and see the palms of the hands </l>
<l rend="indent">in which remain the conch and blood tipped discus</l>
<l>of the small child with the complexion of the blue lily in a high field</l>
<l> who is being raised by the kohl [lined] wide-eyed Yaśodā. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
